vestingNews\\")"}, {"name": "h47", "type": "string", "description": "Heading.text (e.g. \\"ETH Breaks Below $2,000 — Bears in Control\\")"}, {"name": "h48", "type": "string", "description": "Badge.text (e.g. \\"Bearish\\")"}, {"name": "h49", "type": "string", "description": "Text.text (e.g. \\"Ethereum dropped sharply to $1,963 by June 1, then slid further to ~$1,676 intraday on June 5 — down over 14% from May's open. Persistent ETF outflows, a completed death cross, and breakdown below the critical $2,000 psychological support level confirmed bears are firmly in control.\\")"}, {"name": "h50", "type": "json", "description": "KeyValue.items (e.g. [{\\"key\\":\\"Source\\",\\"value\\":\\"Cryptopolitan\\")"}, {"name": "h51", "type": "string", "description": "Heading.text (e.g. \\"Bitcoin Cycle Low at $59K — Standard Chartered\\")"}, {"name": "h52", "type": "string", "description": "Badge.text (e.g. \\"Analysis\\")"}, {"name": "h53", "type": "string", "description": "Text.text (e.g. \\"Standard Chartered senior analyst Geoffrey Kendrick declared Bitcoin's cycle low at $59,000, marking the end of the crypto winter. He cited the SpaceX IPO and a potential U.S.–Iran peace deal as dual catalysts that could trigger the next recovery rally.\\")"}, {"name": "h54", "type": "json", "description": "KeyValue.items (e.g. [{\\"key\\":\\"Source\\",\\"value\\":\\"CoinDesk\\"},{\\"k)"}, {"name": "h55", "type": "string", "description": "Heading.text (e.g. \\"VanEck Files for BNB Spot ETF\\")"}, {"name": "h56", "type": "string", "description": "Badge.text (e.g. \\"ETF News\\")"}, {"name": "h57", "type": "string", "description": "Text.text (e.g. \\"VanEck has filed for a BNB spot ETF, citing BNB's real-world usage, user activity, and revenue generation as differentiators in an increasingly crowded crypto ETF market. The firm argues BNB's fundamentals present a stronger long-term investment case than many blockchain projects still selling a vision.\\")"}, {"name": "h58", "type": "json", "description": "KeyValue.items (e.g. [{\\"key\\":\\"Source\\",\\"value\\":\\"CoinDesk\\"},{\\"k)"}, {"name": "h59", "type": "string", "description": "Heading.text (e.g. \\"BTC ETFs: 13 Straight Days of Outflows\\")"}, {"name": "h60", "type": "string", "description": "Badge.text (e.g. \\"Bearish\\")"}, {"name": "h61", "type": "string", "description": "Text.text (e.g. \\"U.S.-listed spot Bitcoin ETFs recorded 13 consecutive days of net outflows totaling $2.97 billion — the longest streak since launch. The selloff drove 30-day implied volatility to its highest level since early April. However, derivatives data show mildly bullish positioning, suggesting institutional risk appetite is beginning to stabilize.\\")"}, {"name": "h62", "type": "json", "description": "KeyValue.items (e.g. [{\\"key\\":\\"Source\\",\\"value\\":\\"CoinDesk\\"},{\\"k)"}, {"name": "h63", "type": "string", "description": "Section.title (e.g. \\"📊 Market Intelligence\\")"}, {"name": "h64", "type": "string", "description": "Section.description (e.g. \\"Analysis, key metrics, and source data — June 2026\\")"}, {"name": "h65", "type": "string", "description": "Quote.text (e.g. \\"Bitcoin has hit its cycle low at $59,000 — the SpaceX IPO and U.S.–Iran peace talks are the dual catalysts that could end the crypto winter.\\")"}, {"name": "h66", "type": "string", "description": "Quote.author (e.g. \\"Geoffrey Kendrick, Senior Analyst — Standard Chartered\\")"}, {"name": "h67", "type": "string", "description": "Text.text (e.g. \\"Bitcoin is trading around $63,000, recovering from a 4% rally sparked by renewed corporate buying from Michael Saylor. Ethereum has broken below the critical $2,000 level, influenced by persistent ETF outflows and a completed death cross. BTC dominance stands at 58.57%. Total 24h market volume is $66.2B, down 13.3% from prior session. The next leg will be shaped by DeFi regulation, institutional ETF flows, and whether the four-year halving cycle re-asserts itself.\\")"}, {"name": "h68